  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2441080/extras/6b92deb08f5600451db6353eec50242b.avif?t=1707920129\" width=620 height=85 /></span><br>Prepare for an <strong>epic</strong> experience that will leave you <strong>breathless</strong>! In <i>Godsvivors</i>, dive headfirst into a battle of <strong>divine proportions</strong> between the gods of Olympus and the relentless <strong>Hades</strong>. He's threatening the balance of the universe, and it's up to you, fearless player, to take action!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2441080/extras/ee2d9ec8364ef73461d2824f3457e85b.poster.avif?t=1707920129\" width=620 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2441080/extras/ee2d9ec8364ef73461d2824f3457e85b.webm?t=1707920129\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2441080/extras/ee2d9ec8364ef73461d2824f3457e85b.mp4?t=1707920129\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>SLAY THE DEMONS</strong></h2>Prepare for <strong>epic</strong> showdowns with fearsome underworld enemies like the sinister ferryman <strong>Charon</strong> and the god of death himself, <strong>Thanatos</strong>. Improve your skills, unlock divine powers, and face the formidable <strong>Hades</strong>!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2441080/extras/9a8c0a3994f860e2b2be2d817dedca27.poster.avif?t=1707920129\" width=620 height=188 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2441080/extras/9a8c0a3994f860e2b2be2d817dedca27.webm?t=1707920129\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2441080/extras/9a8c0a3994f860e2b2be2d817dedca27.mp4?t=1707920129\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>DIFFERENT GODS TO PLAY!</strong></h2>Choose from seven powerful gods - <strong>Ares, Apollo, Athena, Hephaestus, Hermes, Poseidon, and Zeus</strong> - each with unique abilities and distinct playstyles. Master their tactics, unleash devastating combos, and unleash the true divine power that runs through your veins!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2441080/extras/0e849abd95cb74099d1090c5eaf9dbc5.poster.avif?t=1707920129\" width=620 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2441080/extras/0e849abd95cb74099d1090c5eaf9dbc5.webm?t=1707920129\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2441080/extras/0e849abd95cb74099d1090c5eaf9dbc5.mp4?t=1707920129\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>POWERFUL WEAPONS</strong></h2>The action never stops! In a top-down <strong>roguelite</strong> frenzy of shooting, face endless hordes of demons as you dive into the depths of hell. Arm yourself to the teeth with an impressive variety of weapons, such as pistols, shotguns, rifles, and more. Every strategic choice matters as you face death head-on, fighting to survive for <strong>15 minutes</strong> of pure adrenaline!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2441080/extras/4d5a9ea8e31d3328af03311897d14589.poster.avif?t=1707920129\" width=620 height=188 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2441080/extras/4d5a9ea8e31d3328af03311897d14589.webm?t=1707920129\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2441080/extras/4d5a9ea8e31d3328af03311897d14589.mp4?t=1707920129\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features and Resources</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>7 <strong>Playable</strong> Gods<br></li><li><strong>Unique</strong> Abilities and Playstyles<br></li><li>Devastating <strong>Combos</strong> and Divine <strong>Power</strong><br></li><li>Top-Down Roguelite <strong>Frenzy</strong> of Shooting<br></li><li>Endless Hordes of <strong>Demons</strong><br></li><li>Impressive Variety of <strong>Weapons</strong><br></li><li>Meaningful Strategic <strong>Choices</strong><br></li><li>Epic <strong>Confrontations</strong> with Underworld Enemies<br></li><li>Skills Enhancement and Unlocking <strong>Divine</strong> Powers<br></li><li>Epic Battles between Gods and <strong>Hades</strong><br></li><li>Elimination of Infernal Creatures<br></li><li><strong>15 Minutes</strong> of Adrenaline<br></li><li>Restoration of Order in the Underworld<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Get <i><strong>GODSVIVORS</strong></i> now and embark on an <strong>unforgettable</strong> journey of action and mythology!</h2></li></ul>",
